WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.129 --> 00:00:06.548
All right,
looks like we're clear.

00:00:06.548 --> 00:00:09.676
I can't believe it's
the weekend, and I'm at school!

00:00:09.676 --> 00:00:11.094
This is
the best place to hide.

00:00:11.094 --> 00:00:12.221
Why? Of all the places
we could hide,

00:00:12.221 --> 00:00:13.388
why do I have to sit here
in school?

00:00:13.388 --> 00:00:15.307
Mmph!

00:00:15.307 --> 00:00:16.975
Where's the last place anyone
would think we would hide?

00:00:16.975 --> 00:00:19.311
The scene of our supposed crime,
dummies! We're safe here.

00:00:19.311 --> 00:00:21.438
I'd rather be in jail
than in school.

00:00:21.438 --> 00:00:22.231
[ Door knob rattling ]

00:00:22.231 --> 00:00:24.358
Mm mmph!

00:00:24.358 --> 00:00:25.776
Guys? Guys!

00:00:25.776 --> 00:00:27.444
Stan!

00:00:27.444 --> 00:00:28.946
Guys, thank God!
Just stay right there, Grandpa!

00:00:28.946 --> 00:00:31.240
I know all about the deal.
I know what we have to do.

00:00:31.240 --> 00:00:32.491
How'd you
find us here?

00:00:32.491 --> 00:00:33.784
I figured you guys
were hiding somewhere.

00:00:33.784 --> 00:00:34.743
This is the first place
I thought to look.

00:00:34.743 --> 00:00:36.411
Mm-hmm!

00:00:36.411 --> 00:00:37.537
Yeah, I guess we're dummies,
huh, Kenny?

00:00:37.537 --> 00:00:39.331
Yeah, I guess
 we're dummies.

00:00:39.331 --> 00:00:40.874
Guys, listen --
My stupid grandpa

00:00:40.874 --> 00:00:43.418
and a bunch of other old people
made the deal with ManBearPig.

00:00:43.418 --> 00:00:44.878
It's here because
of their greediness.

00:00:44.878 --> 00:00:46.129
Grandpa:
Everyone's greedy!

00:00:46.129 --> 00:00:47.714
Shut up, Grandpa!

00:00:47.714 --> 00:00:49.216
I know where to go,
but I need your help.

00:00:49.216 --> 00:00:51.510
I'm going to face ManBearPig
and put an end to this deal.

00:00:51.510 --> 00:00:54.554
Are you crazy? We just saw
ManBearPig take down Satan.

00:00:54.554 --> 00:00:55.847
What the hell are we supposed to
do against it?

00:00:55.847 --> 00:00:57.099
We have to try.

00:00:57.099 --> 00:00:58.642
[ Siren wails ]

00:00:58.642 --> 00:01:02.145
Man: Attention school
shooters...again.

00:01:02.145 --> 00:01:05.232
We have you surrounded...again.

00:01:05.232 --> 00:01:07.234
Come out
with your hands up!

00:01:07.234 --> 00:01:11.697
We just sat in school
for nothing.

00:01:11.697 --> 00:01:14.700
Listen!
We know what to do now!

00:01:14.700 --> 00:01:17.286
Drop to the ground and put
your hands on your heads.

00:01:17.286 --> 00:01:19.538
No, I need
to face ManBearPig.

00:01:19.538 --> 00:01:21.873
We have orders!
You're coming with us!

00:01:21.873 --> 00:01:23.333
Yates:
Belay those orders!

00:01:23.333 --> 00:01:28.171
♪♪

00:01:28.171 --> 00:01:32.509
I've been a fool
denying ManBearPig's existence,

00:01:32.509 --> 00:01:35.595
and I didn't realize it
till I went home.

00:01:35.595 --> 00:01:38.974
My wife...had started
a new life without me.

00:01:38.974 --> 00:01:41.059
I wanted to give up,

00:01:41.059 --> 00:01:43.437
but instead,
I robbed a bank in Saint Denis,

00:01:43.437 --> 00:01:45.772
and I went to an island
north of Cuba.

00:01:45.772 --> 00:01:49.276
After I came back, that's
when it all caught up with me.

00:01:49.276 --> 00:01:51.320
All the stagecoaches
I had robbed,

00:01:51.320 --> 00:01:54.364
all the horses I had stole --
for what?!

00:01:54.364 --> 00:01:57.993
We're nothing if we don't
believe in each other!

00:01:57.993 --> 00:02:00.579
And God damn it, it's never
too late to start trying

00:02:00.579 --> 00:02:02.497
to do the right thing.

00:02:02.497 --> 00:02:04.708
You think you know
what that is boys?

00:02:04.708 --> 00:02:06.793
Yes, I do.

00:02:06.793 --> 00:02:08.587
We're going to face
ManBearPig

00:02:08.587 --> 00:02:10.922
and put an end to this deal
once and for all.

